snippet.title: Oddmar - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as Oddmar on an epic journey through a fantastic world inspired by Vikings and Norse mythology in this exciting action-adventure platformer!

Available now for iPad and iPhone:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/oddmar/id1247397901?ls=1&mt=8

Join Oddmar’s community at
http://facebook.com/oddmargame
http://twitter.com/oddmargame
